{"tid":1140559,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"邪到你唔信...丁蟹回歸　港股4月29日起冧市開端？","createTime":"2019-05-06T02:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T06:20:55.000Z","uid":99885,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a9f43e685a690e51ad9562eb5d6558ce3593ef2","tid":1140559,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T02:31:27.000Z","msg":"自從鄭少秋於1992年飾演《大時代》丁蟹角色，播出後適逢港股大冧市，被視為「丁蟹效應」後，鄭少秋每每有新劇上演，甚至僅重播，港股都會聞風色變。若效應持續，2019年4月29日至6月7日，港股又會否劫數難逃？禍不單行的是，剛巧亦是傳統上「五窮六絕」魔咒。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，由鄭少秋主演的《詭探前傳》，將於4月29日晚上播出，預計播到6月7日。 <br />\n<br />\n根據統計，過去鄭少秋只要有新劇播出，港股極大機會遇上災難，例如1992年《大時代》、1994年《笑看風雲》、1995年《男人四十一頭家》、1996年《天地男兒》等。事後均證明「丁蟹效應」不容忽視。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/finance/mobile/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Ffinance%2Fmobile%2Findex.html&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkN%2BPMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=629f08b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/finance/mobile/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"87af1986de5b528ce1d50f01f4d67d080faee049","tid":1140559,"uid":6030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T02:35:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VKAos6QWIcE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVKAos6QWIcE&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkN%2BPMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=99088491\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VKAos6QWIcE</a>"},{"pid":"4a9a796754855ceae5b60da6e571e9dc765fd305","tid":1140559,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87af1986de5b528ce1d50f01f4d67d080faee049","tid":1140559,"uid":6030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T02:35:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VKAos6QWIcE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVKAos6QWIcE&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkN%2BPMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=99088491\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VKAos6QWIcE</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T02:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor